opinions.text:
ORDER
The state’s motion to withdraw the tangible evidence in this case which was introduced by the Attorney-General at defendant’s trial, as prayed, is granted.

attorneys: Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Joel S. Chase, Spec. Asst. Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
John F. Cicilline, Providence, for defendant.
casebody.head_matter:
STATE v. Anthony TASSONE.
No. 78-124-C.A.
Supreme Court of Rhode Island.
March 20, 1980.
Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Joel S. Chase, Spec. Asst. Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
John F. Cicilline, Providence, for defendant.
